# SK DEMO environment trust bundle
#
# Pinned SK ID Solutions ISSUING CA certificates for validating end-user
# authentication certificates returned by the Smart-ID and Mobile-ID APIs.
# These are PUBLIC certificates (no key material). An end-user certificate
# is accepted only if it is DIRECTLY issued (signature-verified) by one of
# the CAs in this bundle — see saebooks_web/eid_providers.py.
#
# Source: SK ID Solutions public CA repository (c.sk.ee / sk.ee), fetched
# 2026-07-12. When SK announces a new issuing CA, append its PEM here.
#

